{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","nameNarration":"御崎 海香","narration":"神浜に不慣れな私に手を貸してくれると@申し出てくれた魔法少女・夏目かこさん","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"彼女は作家としての私を@知っていてくれて…"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21081.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":100,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"夏目 かこ","nameRight":"御崎 海香","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"神浜市には魔女が最近@とても増えてきていて…","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":301101}],"textLeft":"あすなろ市から逃げてきた@魔女っていうのも…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"もしかしたら@関係しているんでしょうか…？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_022.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"どう思いますか？@御崎先生！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":400}],"textRight":"…ど、どうなんでしょう…？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":1}],"textRight":"…ところで、あの@…ひとつお願いが…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_022.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"何でしょうか？@御崎先生"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":300}],"textRight":"その「御崎先生」という@呼び方は…ちょっと…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201}],"textRight":"今は魔法少女としての@御崎海香で…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":0}],"textRight":"しかも、夏目さんには@助けてもらってますし…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301101,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"いえ、そんな！@[chara:301101:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:301101:cheek_0][chara:301101:face_mtn_ex_030.exp.json][chara:301101:lipSynch_1]気になさらなくても…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":401201,"motion":1}],"textRight":"それに、冗談以外では「先生」と@呼ばれるのが苦手というか"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":401201}],"textRight":"担当編集さんとも@約束してるくらいなんです"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face"